{"type": "article", "id": 10001, "title": "Nato 腕带", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-26T07:24:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235402tpl9NKy6cFf4imDn.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t可口可乐与 will.i.am 合作打造的时尚生活时尚品牌 EKOCYCLE 在继和 MCM 合作推出包袋，和Adidas，Beats，LEVI’S 等品牌合作后，最近又和 Misfit 合作推出了特别版的 Nato 腕带。EKOCYCLE 一向推崇环保生活态度，这次也不例外，这些腕带的材料全部来自可口可乐瓶子中的可再生聚酯塑料，在环保的基础上保证时尚度和舒适度。目前单款腕带售价 49.99 美元，三款装则为 99.99 美元，<a href=\"http://store.misfit.com/products\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235359xl5M7ncowXtY4rRg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235359qjZyQ6EgUVKiFkuS.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5525\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235359WptD5mYvE2qIhLGU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235400xU4ZYym3PXNRrvIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235400dmclYEb0Hz1CJ5Xq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523540165xiQ2pNEBJXuvCe.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235401JKmczFs21giupYx6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235402pFvD6LJmSyRfgxGN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55925926\" data-format=\"jpeg